{"tid":699774,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"官方:利馬去馬體會","createTime":"2018-06-12T20:05:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-15T04:31:15.000Z","uid":165817,"like":33,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"8a3f6dea4a0005a8f65b52aa0c745d7de27d2d84","tid":699774,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T20:05:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/13/035718_77a7a59f5854f6d6264d64704019153f.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F13%2F035718_77a7a59f5854f6d6264d64704019153f.jpeg&h=5d298b0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n傳咗阿奴同湊莉久咁耐<br />\n又講到八九千萬身價咁<br />\n<br />\n上年臨尾阿奴出到一億先打動到摩<br />\n點知利馬又睇唔起垃圾奴 唔肯去<br />\n<br />\n摩納哥上年放撚哂所有年輕主力<br />\n就係唔肯放利馬同薛迪比兩個<br />\n估唔到最後係去偏體力化嘅馬體會<br />\n<br />\n摩納哥就陰公<br />\n利馬上季賣到九位數都放唔到/夾硬留<br />\n今年乜成績都冇<br />\n最後仲低過心水價4000萬賣"},{"pid":"198b214073d06e9e6a56b9dbe1466ef656a94ef1","tid":699774,"uid":22993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T20:13:02.000Z","msg":"估唔撚到"},{"pid":"2bb843540cff278c648a9b793d2ab0c999520c7d","tid":699774,"uid":33058,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T20:16:11.000Z","msg":"唔係65M歐咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n摩納哥fatfat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兩季賣既人<br />\n<br />\n利馬 65M<br />\nB施華 42M<br />\n法賓奴 40M<br />\n文迪  好似50？<br />\n包皮  過億<br />\n巴卡約高 ～40M"},{"pid":"1abbe66e80a1789060bf460a7f57d1afc05fbdc8","tid":699774,"uid":46013,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"2bb843540cff278c648a9b793d2ab0c999520c7d","tid":699774,"uid":33058,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T20:16:11.000Z","msg":"唔係65M歐咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n摩納哥fatfat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兩季賣既人<br />\n<br />\n利馬 65M<br />\nB施華 